"Are you sure you want to remove this option?"

"By signing this mandate form, you authorise (A) Volkswagen Payments S.A. to send instructions to your bank to debit your account and (B) your bank to debit your account in accordance with the instructions from Volkswagen Payments S.A."

"As part of your rights, you are entitled to a refund from your bank under the terms and conditions of your agreement with your bank. A refund must be claimed within 8 weeks starting from the date on which your account was debited."
